performers.name: Courtney Algeo
performers.bio: Courtney Algeo loves tacos, video games, her son & husband, mix tapes, and the word "yes." She tells stories for the Minneapolis Institute of Arts.

performers.name: Amina Harper
performers.bio: Amina Harper is a local artist, writer and snack enthusiast. She has contributed to Paper Darts Magazine, The Tangential, MPLSzine and writes a weekly art column for the Daily Planet.

performers.name: Cat Hammond
performers.bio: Cat Hammond writes about gender! He has performed original work most recently in 20% Theatre's The Naked I: Insides Out and Intermedia Arts' Queer Voices reading series.
